Start X containers to form a mnesia cluster
Network Range: 172.19.0.X
Cluster Size : 10

Docker network setup:
docker network create --subnet=172.19.0.0/16 docker_net_1

Create the cluster ip details:
./cluster_config.sh 172.19.0 10

Generate the erlang mnesia cluster sys.config:
./generate_sys_config.esh

Create the docker image:
./build.sh

Start the cluster
./run_cluster.sh docker_net_1

Info:

the erlang nodes are run with longnames, and should use the ip address, to
avoid having to use domain names.

cluster.sys.config is used as the running config, and template.sys.config as the 
template for generating the cluster.sys.config.

To See Mnesia Info:
docker logs CONTAINER_ID